5. Key Ways Data is Stored and Used for Feedback 
    Custom Instructions & GPTs: You can instruct a custom GPT to adhere to feedback stored in its "Instructions" or "Knowledge" files. As the agent acts, you can update these instructions to ensure it avoids past mistakes.
    Conversation Memory: ChatGPT’s ability to recall previous messages in a long chat enables it to "remember" human critiques and improve the output on the second or third attempt.
    Memory Feature: ChatGPT can directly save information across different chat sessions, allowing it to apply feedback permanently to all future interactions. 
